info.senderName: NWS Duluth (Northeast Minnesota and Northern Wisconsin)
info.headline: Wind Advisory issued December 24 at 3:16PM CST until December 25 at 8:00AM CST by NWS Duluth
info.description: ...WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 8 AM CST SUNDAY... * WHAT...Northwest winds 20 to 30 mph with gusts up to 60 mph. * WHERE...Southern Lake and Southern Cook Counties. This includes the Tribal Lands of the Grand Portage Reservation. * WHEN...Until 8 AM CST Sunday. * IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects. Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may result. * ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Strong crosswinds are expected along MN Highway 61.
info.instruction: Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.
